member.summary:
            Represents SignNow document object.
            Document is the fundamental unit of every e-Signature operation.

It contains:


Metadata: file name, size, extension, ID;

Fields, field content elements (texts, checks, signatures, etc...);

Invites, statuses of the invites;

Document ;

members.member:

Whether or not this folder is shared.

/// 
true - it is a shared folder; false - it's not a shared folder.
